			</p>
	
			<p>
				You will need access to an empty MySQL database that will be used by LibreIdP
				to store the following data:
				<ul>
					<li>LibreIdP account information (display name, e-mail address, etc.)</li>
					<li>OAuth access tokens, refresh tokens, authorization codes and code
