					<li>Information about profile pictures</li>
				</ul>
			</p>
	
			<p>
				If you don't have an empty MySQL database for LibreIdP to use, log in to your
				MySQL server and run the command <code>mysqladmin create libreidp</code> as
				<tt>root</tt> to create an empty MySQL database named <tt>libreidp</tt>.
